					<box topPadding="2" leftPadding="4"/>
					<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle">
						<font fontName="Open Sans" size="7" isBold="false"/>
					</textElement>
					<text><![CDATA[Prices in this quotation are valid for 30days, after which The Supplies Mob will requote if required.
Please ensure the quote specifications meets your approval prior to acceptance.
Upon quote acceptance, please email your purchase to orders@thesuppliesmob.com
All goods delivered remain the property of The Supplies Mob until paid for in full.
Any issues with goods supplied must be notified in writing to The Supplies Mob within 7 days of receipt of goods.

For full terms and conditions, please refer to

If you have any questions regarding this quote, please don’t hesitate to reach out.
We look forward to doing business with you.]]></text>
				</staticText>
				<textField hyperlinkType="Reference">
					<reportElement x="154" y="79" width="100" height="20" uuid="57d8164b-218b-41e9-8925-3da95ae57db0"/>
					<textElement markup="none">
						<font fontName="Open Sans" size="7"/>
					</textElement>
					<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["www.thesuppliesmob.com"]]></textFieldExpression>
					<hyperlinkReferenceExpression><![CDATA["www.thesuppliesmob.com"]]></hyperlinkReferenceExpression>
				</textField>
			</band>
		</groupFooter>
